OL,3,CThe charity helping cancer patients
OL,4,Cmeet 13,000 appointments a year
OL,6,FIt was founded in 2006 by Doncaster
OL,7,Fwoman Denise Dunn after she was
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with breast cancer and
OL,9,Fdiscovered that many people were
OL,10,Fstruggling to get to their treatment
OL,11,Fin Sheffield.
OL,13,FThe charity was taken over by her
OL,14,Ffiance, Ian Bacchus, following Miss
OL,15,FDunn's death in 2014.
OL,17,FHe said they provide a lifeline
OL,18,Fservice to many of their clients.
