OL,3,CThe charity helping cancer patients
OL,4,Cmeet 13,000 appointments a year
OL,6,FMr Bacchus said the growing demand is
OL,7,Fpartly due to better technology
OL,8,Fallowing earlier diagnoses.
OL,10,FOne of those who was helped by the
OL,11,Fservice is John Aston, from Doncaster.
OL,12,FHe was diagnosed with prostate cancer
OL,13,Fat the age of 53.
OL,15,F"It's a bus into town, then a train to
OL,16,FSheffield, and then from the train
OL,17,Fstation a bus to Western Park hospital.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
