OL,3,CThe charity helping cancer patients
OL,4,Cmeet 13,000 appointments a year
OL,6,F"I called Firefly and Ian put my mind
OL,7,Fat ease in two minutes. And that was
OL,8,Fit. I had eight weeks of treatment
OL,9,FMonday to Friday."
OL,11,FRick Fuller, a volunteer driver for
OL,12,Fthe charity, said: "It's incredibly
OL,13,Frewarding, picking people up at
OL,14,Farguably the worst point in their
OL,15,Flives and hopefully relieving some of
OL,16,Fthat stress, is what it's all about
OL,17,Fand getting them their safely with no
OL,18,Fworry.
